PrecisAmend Order in Council P.C. 1996-124 of January 25, 1996 which appointed ROBERT G. WRIGHT, of Gloucester, Ontario, as President of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, by revoking the words "for a term of three years" and substituting therefore the words "for a term ending July 25, 1999".
